### Get all items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v2/items

### Get a specific item by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v2/items/P000002

### Get items by item line ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v2/items/itemLine/1
### Get items by item group ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v2/items/itemGroup/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get items by item type ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v2/items/itemType/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get items by supplier ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v2/items/supplier/1
Content-Type: application/json

